{
  "stem": "19921.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Wherever the army goes, the family comes along.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was the reason for us to go to Engel's, to be close to Kolpashev.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as-- the same thing because the front line was approaching, that army was moved out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That army was moved out in September or August and was moved out to Central Asia-- to Central Asia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Central Asia-- that means the-- the main city's Tashkent, and then the surrounding areas-- Samarkand, Namangan-- that's where that army was, closer to the Iranian border.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Closer to the Iranian border.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In any event, so we stayed there in that-- in that-- Krasnyi Iar, and that's where we found out that the army was moved.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, of course, we would have stayed longer because the jobs were good and the pay was all right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Unfortunately, when these incidents occur, we didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we found out where the army is, and they told us, It is in Central Asia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had no problem of getting a ticket, because they didn't cost us any money from the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had our special paper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no provisions on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't give you any food or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't give you any provision of what to do-- what to-- where you should go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But if you want to go to Central Asia, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whenever there is available train, you can go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Central Asia from that thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that incident, we stayed not a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we immediately decided when we discovered that the army moved, we went to pursue it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we pursued that thing here to Central Asia with the trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't have any passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
